highlights.text: “Golden - Acapella” by HUNTR/X, EJAE, AUDREY NUNA, REI AMI, and KPop Demon Hunters Cast is the highest new entry on Top Songs Malaysia at #180.
My Chemical Romance has the most spots on Top Songs Malaysia. “I Don't Love You” is the highest at #16.
“Night Changes” by One Direction has been on Top Songs Malaysia the longest, at 1642 days straight.
“When I Was Your Man” by Bruno Mars is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Malaysia, up 107 spots at #87.
